if SOC_T20

config SPL_T20_USB_BOOT
	bool "T20 SPL: return to mask ROM for USB boot (dev loop)"
	depends on SPL
	help
	  Build the SPL as a mask-ROM USB-boot stage1: bring up the clocks +
	  DDR, run the DM scan, then return to the bootrom (jr ra) instead of
	  loading U-Boot proper from SPI-NOR - how the SPL is brought up and
	  tested on the lab rig. Development only.

endif
